{"tid":2233231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣改革後備動員制度 將成立防衛動員署 後備旅由7個增至12個旅","createTime":"2020-10-07T03:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T16:30:17.000Z","uid":292499,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e8cffde57fce69b97c0f92ab6a6a2bc41bd01550","tid":2233231,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n組織方面，<strong>將成立專責的防衛動員署</strong>，為行政院三級機構；部隊方面，將全台18縣市的地區後備指揮部，以作戰導向合併到作戰區編管，<strong>另現有7個後備旅將增加至12個後備旅</strong>，讓後備戰力越來越強。<br />\n...<br />\n嚴德發說，裝備部分，將使用與常備部隊一致的裝備；訓練部分，更改為1年1訓、1次14天，召訓人數從12萬人增加至26萬人，訓練機構都在建置規劃中，並依序推動。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010070041.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202010070041.aspx&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=6ffa9fe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202010070041.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"113026c86e4d77d6e785484bd1570bc26fcff607","tid":2233231,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e460c0009f5e9be7427809edee57f92481dd75","tid":2233231,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"113026c86e4d77d6e785484bd1570bc26fcff607","tid":2233231,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face